recipesJson.name: Strawberry Chocolate Peanutbutter Cheesecake
recipesJson.author: Freshepies
recipesJson.description:
A rich dark chocolate cheesecake with layers of peanutbutter and sweet strawberries.
Sweeten to taste.

reviews.text: Yo fresh I love vt chocolate mousse. its my favorite chocolate. this recipe is fire i mixed it right after you posted it. just and just tried it. i had to sub in lb strawberry cheesecake cuz i dont have wf but its real tasty. thank you
